  <summary date="2017-11-08T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Beginning Farmer and Rancher Opportunity Act of 2017

 This bill modifies several Department of Agriculture (USDA) programs to authorize additional assistance for beginning farmers and ranchers. The bill modifies USDA programs that address conservation, credit, rural development, research and education, and crop insurance.</summary>
